[[File:Porcelain_crab_Nick_Hobgood.jpg|thumb]]所屬的[[瓷蟹科|瓷蟹科]]雖然有着螃蟹的外表，但其實屬於[[鎧甲蝦總科|鎧甲蝦總科]]，其關係與鎧甲蝦及寄居蟹更為密切。]]
'''蟹化'''（{{lang|en|'''carcinisation'''或'''carcinization'''}}），又名'''短尾化'''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.doc88.com/p-6641639828216.html |title=中华绒螯蟹短尾化发育相关基因筛选 |author=查杰 |date=2009-05-21 |accessdate=2014-09-21 |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2018-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005203842/http://www.doc88.com/p-6641639828216.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是[[演化生物学|演化生物学]]的一個題目，指[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]動物物種在[[演化|演化]]的過程中，從其他樣式演化成為近似蟹類（[[短尾下目|短尾下目]]）相近的形態，特指物種在腹部位置摺疊的變化<ref>{{cite web |url=http://members.jcom.home.ne.jp/natrom/board020902.html#0208211549 |title=タラバガニの進化 |trans_title=堪察加擬石蟹的進化 |language=ja |date=2002-08-21 |accessdate=2014-09-21 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>。這個名詞由{{tsl|en|Lancelot Alexander Borradaile|蘭斯洛特·亞歷山大·巴拉代爾|L. A. Borradaile}}最早提出<ref>{{cite journal |author=Patsy A. McLaughlin & Rafael Lemaitre |year=1997 |title=Carcinization in the anomura – fact or fiction? I. Evidence from adult morphology |journal=[[Contributions_to_Zoology|Contributions to Zoology]] |volume=67 |issue=2 |pages=79–123 |url=http://dpc.uba.uva.nl/ctz/vol67/nr02/art01 |access-date=2014-09-21 |archive-date=2012-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210024757/http://dpc.uba.uva.nl/ctz/vol67/nr02/art01 |dead-url=yes }} [http://decapoda.nhm.org/pdfs/11727/11727.pdf PDF] {{Wayback|url=http://decapoda.nhm.org/pdfs/11727/11727.pdf |date=20120402131842 }}</ref>。

在[[真軟甲亞綱|真軟甲亞綱]][[十足目|十足目]]各個物種裡，有五組生物（特別是[[巨大拟滨蟹|巨大拟滨蟹]]）曾各自獨立發生過蟹化過程<ref>{{cite journal |author=J. Keiler, S. Richter, C.S. Wirkner |year=2013 |title=Evolutionary Morphology of the Hemolymph Vascular System in Hermit and King Crabs (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomala) |journal=[[Journal_of_Morphology|Journal of Morphology]] |volume=274 |issue=7 |pages=759–778 |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/jmor.20133/pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |doi=10.1002/jmor.20133 |language=en |access-date=2014-09-21 |archive-date=2016-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316100753/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/jmor.20133/pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個轉變，科學家認為結果演變出[[寄居蟹|寄居蟹]]的祖先出來。
另一個例子是[[瓷蟹科|瓷蟹科]]，其物種雖然有着螃蟹的外表，但其實屬於[[鎧甲蝦總科|鎧甲蝦總科]]，其關係與鎧甲蝦<ref>{{cite journal |author=J. Keiler, S. Richter, C.S. Wirkner |year=2014 |title=Evolutionary morphology of the organ systems in squat lobsters and porcelain crabs (crustacea: Decapoda: Anomala): An insight into carcinization |journal=[[Journal_of_Morphology|Journal of Morphology]] |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/jmor.20311/pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |language=en |doi=10.1002/jmor.20311 |access-date=2014-09-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307224656/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/jmor.20311/pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[陆寄居蟹|陆寄居蟹]]、[[椰子蟹|椰子蟹]]（{{lang|la|''Birgus latro''}}）及螃蟹更為密切<ref>{{cite journal |author=C. L. Morrison, A. W. Harvey, S. Lavery, K. Tieu, Y. Huang & C. W. Cunningham |year=2001 |title=Mitochondrial gene rearrangements confirm the parallel evolution of the crab-like form |journal=[[Proceedings_of_the_Royal_Society_B:_Biological_Sciences|Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences]] |volume=269 |issue=1489 |pages=345–350 |url=http://www.biology.duke.edu/cunningham/pdfs/Morrison%20et%20al.pdf |doi=10.1098/rspb.2001.1886 |pmid=11886621 |pmc=1690904 |access-date=2014-09-21 |archive-date=2010-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610111946/http://www.biology.duke.edu/cunningham/pdfs/Morrison%20et%20al.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

